reviewText: I REALLY CAN'T GIVE A REVIEW OF THIS MOVIE, BECAUSE I NEVER GOT A CHANCE TO SEE IT, IT WOULD NOT PLAY ON ANY OF MY DVD PLAYERS, I REALLY HATE THAT BECAUSE I REALLY WANTED TO SEE THIS MOVIE, GEE I FEEL CHEATED,,YOU DON'T HAVE ANY WAY OF KNOWING  IF THE DVD'S WILL PLAY ON YOUR PLAYERS OR NOT.
